text:
A message from The Empty Summit:
The Nothing
Is not you.

DH Lawrence prophesied Wokeness so hard: 
“What then is Moby Dick? He is the deepest blood-being of the white race; he is our deepest blood nature. / And he is hunted, hunted, hunted, by the maniacal fanaticism of our white mental consciousness.”

Using only Masonic Arithmetic (triangulation and digital reduction)
0 > 0
1 > 1
2 > 3
3 > 6 > 21 > 3
4 > 10 > 1
5 > 15 > 6 
6  > 21 > 3
7 > 28 > 10 > 1
8 > 36 > 9
9 > 45 > 9 ...

... so the four basins, and their tributaries, are 
[0] 0
[1] 1, 4, 7
[3 / 6] 2, 3, 5, 6
[9] 8, 9 ...

... Thus an esoteric Tetraktys:
0
8, 9
1, 4, 7
2, 3, 5, 6 
- The Empty Summit

... "... We want to hunt him down. ... And in this maniacal conscious hunt of ourselves we get dark races and pale to help us, red, yellow, and black, east and west, Quaker and fire worshipper ... in this ghastly maniacal hunt which is our doom and our suicide."

Hermes to Prometheus in Aeschylus: “… Look for no term / To such an agony till there stand forth / Among the Gods one who shall take upon him / Thy sufferings and consent to enter hell / Far from the light of Sun, yea, the deep pit / And mirk of Tartarus, for thee.” ...
... What the hell is going on here? I thought I had a (tentative) grip on this myth.
Thanks, will investigate. (Trying not to find being saved by a centaur staggeringly embarrassing.)
